name: Savanna Dry Goods X Wanda Lephoto

metadata.name: SWL Yellow Trench Coat With Plaid Patch Work #1/1
metadata.description:
SAVANNA WANDA LEPHOTO

As an extension of the Dry Goods range and as way to bring it into the Metaverse, Savanna asked Wanda Lephoto to create a set of 1-of-1 original garments, that were 3D modelled and rendered into digital collectables. So, if you want the garment, you have to get the NFT. Only available to persons over 18. All proceeds go to GreenUp.

Savanna Yellow Trench Coat With 2 Savanna Acacia Tree and Plaid Patch Work
- Button Closure
- Front and Back Logo
- No Lining
- Central Vent at Back

80% Polyester 20% Nylon
